{"tid":1326332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌我真係好撚嬲 大家咪撚笑 同埋要大家比意見","createTime":"2019-07-17T07:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:57:56.000Z","uid":267229,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21b64076e4a15eb2bca529169cfe87710c8cfc48","tid":1326332,"uid":267229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"我係一個外賣仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n今日送左一單去一間office到<br />\n係到等lift嗰陣 隔離就企左個靚女OL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係幾正 （咪撚問我攞圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n之後同佢入左同一部lift<br />\n咁啱佢又企正係我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係企到勁埋嗰隻<br />\n雖然我眼係向前望<br />\n但係我好肯定佢一直係到望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就肯定有小小暗爽<br />\n嗰陣心諗條女係咪冧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後尾我就同其他人出左lift<br />\n點知發覺自己出錯左<br />\n跟住就即刻禁返住部lift<br />\n就起lift門開嗰一剎那<br />\n我聽撚到同望撚到條女同隔離條仔<br />\n講我塊面有好撚大粒瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似就爆 好乸核突<br />\n勁驚會噴到自己<br />\n我嗰下真係差啲屌出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而條女見到我嗰下都嚇撚左一下<br />\n之後我入左lift自己企埋係個角落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地就係到扮禁電話<br />\n屌你老母真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打有無咩暗瘡膏或者洗面奶好推薦<br />\n屌 宜家睇到粒瘡又真係幾大粒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\non99<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a291010eac92e7f888192276ab47fc8be34a0f7","tid":1326332,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"有無瘡圖"},{"pid":"5f497e7f8e33999b3d2be82348ed45ff922b438f","tid":1326332,"uid":74162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"唔爭氣咁笑左"},{"pid":"8dc667525a9c14db45427bdbf9c2e74948da0261","tid":1326332,"uid":199649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"有濃的定係冇濃 有難搞好多"},{"pid":"2d1d0b8b80647e3db8997d4f0e8d2fba8ef3e978","tid":1326332,"uid":267229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dc667525a9c14db45427bdbf9c2e74948da0261","tid":1326332,"uid":199649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"有濃的定係冇濃 有難搞好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"有小小"},{"pid":"260546c937cc677ce2fb9c1e8befeb8ddc142642","tid":1326332,"uid":267229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a291010eac92e7f888192276ab47fc8be34a0f7","tid":1326332,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"有無瘡圖"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"陣線po"},{"pid":"0a5d48ae2931a06e390e27fc2920ac2aedbc2733","tid":1326332,"uid":267229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"260546c937cc677ce2fb9c1e8befeb8ddc142642","tid":1326332,"uid":267229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a291010eac92e7f888192276ab47fc8be34a0f7","tid":1326332,"uid":122134